---
title: Nan's Cheesy Pork & Bacon Lasagne with Cucumber Salad
description: Have you ever had a saucy pork mince in a lasagne, we would love to try it out. Let’s whip one up with bacon and a Parmesan
cheese mash topping. The layers of ragu will create a lasagne that everyone will be raving about.
